'''''King Solomon's Mines''''' ni film yasohotse muri 1985 , iturutse kuri novel yitwa King Solomon's Mines yanditswe na  H. Rider yajonjogoye<ref>Found: Fresh Clues to Mystery of King Solomon's Mines (nationalgeographic.com)</ref> . Irimo Richard Chamberlain, Sharon Stone, Herbert Lom na John Rhys-Davies<ref>King Solomon's Mines | novel by Haggard | Britannica <nowiki>https://www.britannica.com</nowiki> › ... › Fictional Characters</ref> . Yahinduwe na Gene Quintano na James R. Silke kandi iyobowe na J. Lee Thompson<ref>King Solomon's Mines (Allan Quatermain, #1) by ... - Goodreads <nowiki>https://www.goodreads.com</nowiki> › book › show › 23814.Ki...</ref> . Iyi verisiyo yinkuru yari yoroheje,  urwenya, iganisha ku  gusebya ''Indiana Jones'' (aho umukinnyi wa francise Rhys-Davies yagaragaye mubice bibiri). Yafatiwe amashusho hanze ya [[Harare]] muri [[Zimbabwe]] . <ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0089421/locations?ref_=tt_dt_dt</ref>

Yakurikiwe nuruhererekane ''[[:en:Allan_Quatermain_and_the_Lost_City_of_Gold|Allan Quatermain and the Lost City of Gold]]'' (1986) kandi yagombaga gukurikirwa nuruhererekane rutigeze rukorwa<ref>The Search Continues for King Solomon's Mines - HISTORY <nowiki>https://www.history.com</nowiki> › news › the-search-continues-...</ref>, igerageza ry'ambere ryaba rishingiye kuri ''She na Allan'', ikindi gitabo cya Haggard<ref>King Solomon's Mines (2004) | BFI <nowiki>https://www2.bfi.org.uk</nowiki> › films-tv-people</ref>, hanyuma kugerageza bwa kabiri kwitwa ''Allan Quatermain na Jewel of the East'' kandi iyobowe na producer Golan.<ref>King Solomon's Mines, by H. Rider Haggard <nowiki>https://www.pagebypagebooks.com</nowiki> › H_Rider_Haggard</ref>

